Package: PCBN
Title: Create and sample pair-copula Bayesian networks not requiring integration
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Niels", "Horsman", , "niels.horsman@hotmail.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Is able to create and sample pair-copula Bayesian networks not requiring integration.
    That is, it uses graphs with no active cycles or interfering v-structures.
    Furthermore, it can fit a PCBN to a data set using a hill climbing alogrithm.
License: What license is it under?
